reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice for the money
reviews.reviewText: Interchangeable Seasonal Welcome Sign Front Door Decoration, Rustic Round Wood Wreaths Wall.,I read a few of the complaints and some had nothing to do with the product itself so I discounted them and took a chance. I'm glad I did. This is definitely wood with a laminate on top which is fine, the magnets are cute and hold well the greenery is plastic just what you'd expect and if I had a complaint at all it would be the bow. The bow is potato sack material and lies flat I inserted very thin wire through the material to fluff it up and that worked to an extent but overall this is a nice decoration for indoors. Outdoors is another story like anything else the weather is merciless so for me not recommended to use out doors

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love it! It’s so pretty and well made. I love the concept. It makes it so easy to change out decor with the seasons!The bow and greenery is a little smashed once it arrives. This is to be expected but with a little work it takes shape again.I purchased two for gifts.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super cute and works for all year
reviews.reviewText: It’s good material. Wind, snow and rain proof. I recently had a winter storm in my town and I forgot to take it off the door and it perfectly stayed on with no problem. No chipping to the paint or fake leaves or anything. And the magnet is surprisingly strong.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Perfect for us busy moms who have other things to get done and can’t decorate like a pintrest star. Easy to hang, easy to change. Super cute and does the trick!

reviews.reviewText: I bought 2 of these and I will be ordering another for myself asap. I got these as Christmas gifts and I think they are so cute! reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars It's just okay
reviews.reviewText: This is nice but there are flaws. I cut out the bow and replaced it with one of my own. It was too smashed and unappealing when it arrived. The letters H, M, E are not lined up. When I put the seasonal decoration in the middle to make the O, it looks okay. These are interchangeable with a magnet which works fine. Would I purchase this again or for someone else? No. But I kept it because it looks okay in the space where I hung it.

reviews.reviewTitle: Está bonita pero pensé si era madera
